Class CloseableForwardingKVStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.permazen.kv.util.ForwardingKVStore
      • io.permazen.kv.util.CloseableForwardingKVStore

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class CloseableForwardingKVStore
extends ForwardingKVStore
implements CloseableKVStore
    A ForwardingKVStore also implementing CloseableKVStore, with some associated underlying Closeable resource to close when close()'d.
